original_title: ZZ Top: Live at Stagecoach Festival
overview: This is professionally shot footage of the ZZ Top performance at the Stagecoach California's Country Music Festival on April 26th, 2015. The band's set-list was a follows:  01:06​ - Got Me Under Pressure  05:14​ - Waitin' for the bus / Jesus Just Left Chicago  12:48​ - Gimme All Your Lovin'  17:40​ - I'm Bad, I'm Nationwide  22:18​ - Pincushion  26:38​ - I Gotsta Get Paid  30:34​ - Flyin' High  35:12​ - Foxy Lady  39:14​ - Catfish Blues  45:46​ - Cheap Sunglasses  49:55​ - Chartreuse  53:18​ - Sharp Dressed Man  58:03​ - Legs  1:03:44​ - La Grange  1:11:50​ - Tush
title: ZZ Top: Live at Stagecoach Festival
